==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Taxer
<hw>Tax"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
taxes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One of two officers chosen yearly to regulate the
assize of bread, and to see the true gauge of weights and measures is
observed.</def> <mark>[Camb. Univ., Eng.]</mark> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>taxor</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Taxgatherer</ent>⟦br⟧
